---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Frame1 from '../images/depoimentos/Frame 1.svg';
import Frame2 from '../images/depoimentos/Frame 2.svg';
import Frame3 from '../images/depoimentos/Frame 3.svg';
---

<section class="py-24 px-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-950/30 to-slate-900">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">
        <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-blue-200 to-orange-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
          Quem já transformou sua empresa
        </span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          <!-- SVG Star -->
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <!-- SVG Quote -->
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M7 17H11V10L4 10V17H8L7 21M13 17H17V10L10 10V17H14L13 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "A TuCont transformou completamente minha visão sobre contabilidade. Deixou de ser um centro de custo e burocracia para se tornar uma ferramenta estratégica que impulsionou nosso crescimento em 38% no último ano."
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <Image 
            src={Frame1} 
            alt="Camila Rodrigues"
            width={48}
            height={48}
            class="rounded-full border-2 border-blue-400/50"
          />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Camila Rodrigues</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">CEO, Innovate Solutions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M7 17H11V10L4 10V17H8L7 21M13 17H17V10L10 10V17H14L13 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "Os frameworks da Jornada Empresarial foram decisivos para identificarmos gargalos fiscais que drenavam nosso capital. Após implementar as soluções sugeridas, reduzimos nossa carga tributária em 22% de forma totalmente legal e segura."
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <Image 
            src={Frame3} 
            alt="Ricardo Oliveira"
            width={48}
            height={48}
            class="rounded-full border-2 border-blue-400/50"
          />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Ricardo Oliveira</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">CFO, Future Retail</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-slate-800/50 backdrop-blur-xl border border-slate-700/50 rounded-3xl p-6 hover:bg-slate-800/70 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-1 mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-yellow-400 fill-current" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-400 mb-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M7 17H11V10L4 10V17H8L7 21M13 17H17V10L10 10V17H14L13 21" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
        
        <p class="text-slate-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          "Mais que um contador, a TuCont se tornou um parceiro estratégico do nosso negócio. As conexões que fizemos através do marketplace exclusivo nos abriram portas para novos mercados e parcerias que jamais teríamos acesso de outra forma."
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <Image 
            src={Frame2} 
            alt="Mariana Alves"
            width={48}
            height={48}
            class="rounded-full border-2 border-blue-400/50"
          />
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-white">Mariana Alves</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Fundadora, Green Ventures</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Corrigindo a classe text-transparent que estava escrita como text-transparent */
  .text-transparent {
    color: transparent;
  }
</style>